<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta name="csrf-token" content={Phoenix.Controller.get_csrf_token()} />
    <title>Confidential Computation - Exclosured</title>
    <style>
      * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
      body {
        font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
        background: #0f0f23;
        color: #e0e0e0;
        min-height: 100vh;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 1100px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
      }
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      }
      .header h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
        color: #7bed9f;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      }
      .header p {
        color: #888;
        font-size: 1rem;
        max-width: 640px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        line-height: 1.5;
      }
      .panels {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 2rem;
      }
      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .panels { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      }
      .panel {
        background: #1a1a2e;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border: 1px solid #2a2a4a;
      }
      .panel h2 {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        color: #7bed9f;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
      }
      label {
        display: block;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        color: #aaa;
        margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
      }
      input[type="password"],
      input[type="text"] {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 0.7rem 1rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        border: 1px solid #333;
        background: #16213e;
        color: #eee;
        font-size: 1rem;
        outline: none;
        transition: border-color 0.2s;
      }
      input:focus {
        border-color: #7bed9f;
      }
      .result-box {
        margin-top: 1rem;
        padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        background: #16213e;
        border: 1px solid #2a2a4a;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        min-height: 2.4rem;
      }
      .result-box.server {
        border-color: #e94560;
      }
      .result-label {
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      .result-label.browser { color: #7bed9f; }
      .result-label.server { color: #e94560; }

      /* Strength bar */
      .strength-bar-container {
        margin-top: 0.8rem;
        height: 8px;
        background: #2a2a4a;
        border-radius: 4px;
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .strength-bar {
        height: 100%;
        border-radius: 4px;
        transition: width 0.3s, background 0.3s;
      }
      .strength-bar.weak { background: #e94560; }
      .strength-bar.fair { background: #f9a825; }
      .strength-bar.strong { background: #7bed9f; }
      .strength-bar.very_strong { background: #00e676; }

      /* Data flow diagram */
      .data-flow {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        margin-top: 1.2rem;
        padding: 0.8rem;
        background: #12122a;
        border-radius: 8px;
      }
      .flow-box {
        padding: 0.5rem 0.8rem;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        text-align: center;
        min-width: 120px;
      }
      .flow-box.browser-box {
        background: rgba(123, 237, 159, 0.12);
        border: 1px solid #7bed9f;
        color: #7bed9f;
      }
      .flow-box.server-box {
        background: rgba(233, 69, 96, 0.12);
        border: 1px solid #e94560;
        color: #e94560;
      }
      .flow-arrow {
        color: #555;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        flex-shrink: 0;
      }
      .flow-detail {
        font-size: 0.65rem;
        margin-top: 0.2rem;
        opacity: 0.8;
      }

      /* Server log */
      .server-log {
        margin-top: 2.5rem;
        background: #1a1a2e;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border: 1px solid #2a2a4a;
      }
      .server-log h2 {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: #e94560;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      .log-entries {
        max-height: 200px;
        overflow-y: auto;
        font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Fira Code', monospace;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
      }
      .log-entry {
        padding: 0.4rem 0.6rem;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #1f1f3a;
        color: #ccc;
        display: flex;
        gap: 0.6rem;
      }
      .log-entry .timestamp {
        color: #666;
        flex-shrink: 0;
      }
      .log-entry .event-name {
        color: #e94560;
        flex-shrink: 0;
      }
      .log-entry .event-data {
        color: #7bed9f;
        word-break: break-all;
      }
      .empty-log {
        color: #555;
        font-style: italic;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
      }
      .status-badge {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
        border-radius: 4px;
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      .status-badge.loading {
        background: rgba(249, 168, 37, 0.2);
        color: #f9a825;
      }
      .status-badge.ready {
        background: rgba(123, 237, 159, 0.2);
        color: #7bed9f;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>&#128274; Confidential Computation</h1>
        <p>
          Sensitive data (passwords, SSNs) is processed entirely in client-side
          WASM. The server only receives masked or computed results -- never the
          raw secrets.
        </p>
      </div>
      <%= @inner_content %>
    </div>
    <script defer phx-track-static src={"/assets/app.js"}></script>
  </body>
</html>
